name: The Tickle monster
description: You are in luck, you found SCP-999's room.  SCP-999 engulfs you and tickles you.  SCP-999 will protect you. SCP-999 loves you.  SCP-999 is your very best friend.  SCP-999 is life.  Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle, Tickle!
